title: MONDAY 3/8 - Another Eagle leaving the nest?
itunes:title: MONDAY 3/8 - Another Eagle leaving the nest?
description:
Carson Wentz has already been dealt from the Eagles, now it looks like Tight End Zach Ertz (0:09) could be on the move as well. JuJu Smith-Schuster not likely to return to Pittsburgh (0:59). Chargers linebacker Denzel Perryman ready to hit the free agent market (1:33) and Kliff Kingsbury (1:59) talks about adding another receiving threat to the Cardinals offense
